{"tid":1729044,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"木亥","createTime":"2019-11-17T06:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T12:27:48.000Z","uid":294707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eae50cd55b279e38ef26ca60466030275e7cbdb9","tid":1729044,"uid":294707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"今日我睇睇吓個舊post突然睇到個字<br />\n所以上網search吓...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.rfi.fr/tw/%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B/20180222-20%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%258F%2596%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%259C%258B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%2525E4%2525B8%2525AD%2525E5%25259C%25258B%2F20180222-20%2525E5%2525B9%2525B4%2525E5%2525BE%25258C%2525E4%2525B8%2525AD%2525E5%25259C%25258B%2525E5%2525B0%252587%2525E5%25258F%252596%2525E4%2525BB%2525A3%2525E7%2525BE%25258E%2525E5%25259C%25258B%2525E6%252588%252590%2525E7%252582%2525BA%2525E6%25259C%252580%2525E5%2525A4%2525A7%2525E6%2525A0%2525B8%2525E9%25259B%2525BB%2525E5%25259C%25258B&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=22a544eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.rfi.fr/tw/%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B/20180222-20%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%258F%2596%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%259C%258B</a><br />\n<br />\n <em><span style=\"color: blue;\">中國將在2030年取代美國，成為全球最大核能國家。<br />\n...<br />\n到2040年，核電在中國總電力供應中的比重將達到4%，高於2016年為2%。2040年，所有類型的總電力供應將達到3,188千兆瓦，較2016年的1,625千兆瓦提高一倍。這意味着核電裝機容量將較2016年的32.5千兆瓦增長兩倍多，至127.52千兆瓦。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n當台灣係咁放棄核能嘅時候，然後內地大大力發展核能，跟據國內過住豆腐渣工程，同對求成績而唔計質素...我有d擔心...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734b5dd2c80017cc2cbc822bda666d703b9d29ee","tid":1729044,"uid":9062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"係咪指核事故？<br />\n核污染？"},{"pid":"39587fc721d664b12d64e7aaeec58b68c2bf164f","tid":1729044,"uid":294707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"734b5dd2c80017cc2cbc822bda666d703b9d29ee","tid":1729044,"uid":9062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"係咪指核事故？<br />\n核污染？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:24:03.000Z","msg":"我唔識咖<br />\n唔好誤會<br />\n只係資料蒐集一下"},{"pid":"9a60bd5eaef411315851d546fd02bfbcae596a90","tid":1729044,"uid":185066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"唔好玩啦 中國有2030先算啦 而且我地未去到前已經吸tg毒氣吸死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df1c09b409fd0aa1bcb53c4edc7e6849e493d1d","tid":1729044,"uid":294707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:27:48.000Z","msg":"生輻射寶寶"}]}